"title": "5319: fugitives",
"media_type": "Text",
"index_reference": "5319: fugitives",
"language": "eng",
"review_level": "None",
"content": "<p>People fleeing, especially from persecution or punishment and seeking refuge. The OT makes special provision for the needs of such people.</p>\n<h2>Fugitives are those in flight</h2>\n<h3>From family</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen35:1\">GEN 35:1</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen35:7\">GEN 35:7</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Judg9:21\">JDG 9:21</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Sam13:34\">2SA 13:34</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Sam15:13-2Sam15:15\">2SA 15:13–15:15</a></p>\n<h3>From war</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Sam24:13\">2SA 24:13</a></strong>; <strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Obad1:14\">OBA 1:14</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev26:36\">LEV 26:36</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Num21:29\">NUM 21:29</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Josh8:20\">JOS 8:20</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Josh8:22\">JOS 8:22</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Sam10:14\">2SA 10:14</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer46:22\">JER 46:22</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer48:19\">JER 48:19</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek17:21\">EZK 17:21</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek24:26\">EZK 24:26</a></p>\n<h3>From other people</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod2:15\">EXO 2:15</a></strong>; <strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt2:13\">MAT 2:13</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod14:27\">EXO 14:27</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam22:17\">1SA 22:17</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs2:39\">1KI 2:39</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs11:40\">1KI 11:40</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa15:5\">ISA 15:5</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa15:9\">ISA 15:9</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa45:20\">ISA 45:20</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer48:6\">JER 48:6</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer48:45\">JER 48:45</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt24:15-Matt24:20\">MAT 24:15–24:20</a> parallels <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark13:14-Mark13:17\">MRK 13:14–13:17</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke21:21-Luke21:23\">LUK 21:21–21:23</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts8:1\">ACT 8:1</a></p>\n<h3>From vengeance</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer50:28\">JER 50:28</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen4:14\">GEN 4:14</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job15:22\">JOB 15:22</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov28:17\">PRO 28:17</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer44:14\">JER 44:14</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer48:19\">JER 48:19</a></p>\n<h2>Comfort for the fugitives</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa21:14\">ISA 21:14</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Num35:6\">NUM 35:6</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut23:15\">DEU 23:15</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa16:3-Isa16:4\">ISA 16:3–16:4</a></p>",
